title: Texas Roadhouse Shares Gain After Upbeat Start to Quarter
description: Texas Roadhouse Inc. shares climbed after the company reported robust sales growth for the start of the first quarter, even as fourth-quarter same-store sales fell short of Wall Street forecasts.
